{"tid":1848380,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港「沙士」無阻觀眾入戲院睇大片","createTime":"2020-01-28T12:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T10:05:06.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"96e23d457a8abf375ef0ce9125c85dccdcf6ed51","tid":1848380,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"2013年3至5月, 係「沙士」最肆虐香港的時期, 5月24日才首現「零感染」. &nbsp; 係果段時間, 香港戲院票房基本慘淡, 有唔少零票房電影.<br />\n但奇在「沙士」無阻唔少觀眾入戲院睇大片. &nbsp;《特務戇J》和《變種特攻2》先後在4月上映, 結果《變種特攻2》票房收近1400萬, 《特務戇J》票房都超過1000萬. &nbsp;5月上映的《22世紀殺人網絡:決戰未來》票房依然有2677萬.<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎,&nbsp; 「沙士」會危害大部分電影既票房, 但大片不愁沒有觀眾. 相信「武漢肺炎」都係咁.<br />\n<br />\n蘋果曾訪問沙士下入戲院既觀眾.<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20030505/3271896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20030505%2F3271896&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=79e2712d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20030505%2F3271896&h=09c00b21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20030505/3271896</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>而昨日記者便到銅鑼灣UA時代戲院，發現不少觀眾無懼SARS威脅入場欣賞電影，其中《變種特攻2》便有不少觀眾捧場，觀眾陳小姐說：「唔驚得咁多，而且睇過第一集，咪睇埋第二集囉。」</strong>此外，白韻琴和謝偉俊亦結伴欣賞《特務戇J》，兩人更沒戴口罩上街，但白姐姐就表示不擔心受感染。 採訪：何永寧 攝影：何國豪"},{"pid":"43ddad10eba21c6f944b8db6d85b0d313cc9ddc6","tid":1848380,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2013年3至5月</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">, 係「沙士」最肆虐香港的時期, 5月24日才首現「零感染」.   係果段時間, 香港戲院票房基本慘淡, 有唔少零票房電影.<br />\n但奇在「沙士」無阻唔少觀眾入戲院睇大片.  《特務戇J》和《變種特攻2》先後在4月上映, 結果《變種特攻2》票房收近1400萬, 《特務戇J》票房都超過1000萬.  5月上映的《22世紀殺人網絡:決戰未來》票房依然有2677萬.<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎,  「沙士」會危害大部分電影既票房, 但大片不愁沒有觀眾. 相信「武漢肺炎」都係咁.<br />\n<br />\n蘋果曾訪問沙士下入戲院既觀眾.<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20030505/3271896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20030505%2F3271896&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=79e2712d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20030505%2F3271896&h=09c00b21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20030505/3271896</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>而昨日記者便到銅鑼灣UA時代戲院，發現不少觀眾無懼SARS威脅入場欣賞電影，其中《變種特攻2》便有不少觀眾捧場，觀眾陳小姐說：「唔驚得咁多，而且睇過第一集，咪睇埋第二集囉。」</strong>此外，白韻琴和謝偉俊亦結伴欣賞《特務戇J》，兩人更沒戴口罩上街，但白姐姐就表示不擔心受感染。 採訪：何永寧 攝影：何國豪</span></blockquote><br />\n下次cut埋個日期先post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74269eae16add6c962fb6b4b83fbf56ed8456c97","tid":1848380,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"所以《猛禽暴隊：解瘋小丑女》係香港多數會繼續賣座<br />\n<br />\n其他電影? 有可能零票房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/5papVJj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5papVJj.jpg&h=bd4f67f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e39c7d8de8b225a2259075c07934d6f6e2e0110e","tid":1848380,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"Fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a70154732e6f5de317f928b83ed0c93201894c7","tid":1848380,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"43ddad10eba21c6f944b8db6d85b0d313cc9ddc6","tid":1848380,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">201